		"notes": "\n\t<p><i>This enormous, corpulent toad-man squats atop a golden throne, held aloft by naked, vacant-eyed human thralls.</i></p>\n\t<p></p>\n\t<p><strong>AC</strong> 9, <strong>HP</strong> 48, <strong>ATK</strong> 1 bite +6 (1d8) or 1 croaking doom or 2 spell +8, <strong>MV</strong> close, <strong>S</strong> +3, <strong>D</strong> -1, <strong>C</strong> +3, <strong>I</strong> +4, <strong>W</strong> +4, <strong>Ch</strong> +2, <strong>AL</strong> <strong>C</strong>, <strong>LV</strong> 10</p><p></p>\n\t<p><strong>Croaking Doom</strong>. 1/hour. All non-Zlann-Yi within double near DC 16 CON or paralyzed 1d4 rounds. If target is LV 7 or less and fails check, go to 0 HP.</p><p></p><p><strong>Enslave (INT spell)</strong>. DC 15. One target within double near DC 15 WIS or Zlann-Yi sorcerer-king controls for 2d6 rounds.</p><p></p><p><strong>Haruspicy (WIS spell)</strong>. DC 13. After taking 1 round to read the entrails of a sentient creature, all Zlann-Yi within near have ADV on all ATK rolls and checks for 1d6 rounds.</p><p></p><p><strong>Summon Toad Demon</strong>. 1/day. Summons a toad demon to serve for 2d6 rounds.</p><p></p><p><strong>Teleport (INT spell)</strong>. Self. DC 14. Teleport up to 10 miles.</p><p></p><p><strong>Terrify (WIS spell)</strong>. DC 15. On target within double near DC 15 WIS or DISADV on ATK rolls for 1d6 rounds.</p><p></p><p><strong>Unholy Blight (WIS spell)</strong>. DC 15. All enemies in a near-sized cube within far take 4d6 damage.</p><p></p><p><strong>Warding (INT spell)</strong>. Self. DC 14. Can only be harmed by magical sources for 1d4 rounds.</p><p></p>",
